text: Up on @realmoney @Seabreezelp seabreezepartnerslp.com/fund… Jun 21, 2022 | 08:22 AM EDT DOUG KASS When the Time Comes To Buy, You Won't Want To * In the last six months, the Polyannas have become Cassandras as "Group Stink" and general market expectations have materially turned

bearish * Do not invest in the present - looking at the rear view mirror is sub optimal as equities are a discounting mechanism * Future rates of change moves stocks * While Bear Markets are borne out of good news (late 2021), Bull markets are borne out of bad news (now/soon?)
